timeline.body: Aren't these added regions part of the Myths' Guild dungeon? I know most of the wiki refers to it as the Corsair Cove Dungeon, but most players will not recognize it as such. [Konar even refers to it as the "Myths' Guild Dungeon" when a task is assigned there.](https://github.com/runelite/runelite/blob/master/runelite-client/src/main/java/net/runelite/client/plugins/slayer/Task.java#L216)

timeline.body:
Why doesn't this include 9360, 9616, 10381, 10382, or 10384? (103883 looks like a typo and should be changed to 10383) I also don't see the Kruk fight region included in here.

11662 is the Maniacal Monkey hunter area, not part of Kruk's dungeon.

timeline.body:
The wiki names this the Northern Tundras, or the Frozen Tundra of the North. I think Northern Tundras is a better name to go with here?

6461 should probably be separately labeled Wintertodt Camp.

This should include 9264 since the only accessible part of that region is in Kandarin.

9778 should be the Ourania Hunter area.
Maybe 10549 should be labeled as the Ranging Guild?
10550 should be McGrubor's Wood.
10804 should be the Legends' Guild.
Maybe 10807 should be Sinclair Mansion?
